                         <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-center">One Can vs. Daily Recommendation</h3>
                         <p class="text-sm text-center mb-4 text-gray-600">The World Health Organization (WHO) recommends no more than 25g (about 6 teaspoons) of added sugar per day for optimal health. A single can of cola far exceeds that limit.</p>
