                                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-[#FFD166]">40 Minutes: Caffeine Hit</h4>
                                        <p>Caffeine absorption is complete. Your pupils dilate, blood pressure rises, and your liver dumps more sugar into your bloodstream. Adenosine receptors in your brain are blocked, preventing drowsiness.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#FFD166] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl mx-auto my-4 md:my-0 flex-shrink-0 relative">40'</div>
